      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Your existence does not belong to society to consume; it was born from a deeper source and has inherent value beyond mere utility. The quiet you seek only isolates you from the genuine connections that could finally make this burden feel worth lifting. Do you truly wish to trade the heavy noise of survival for a silence that offers no warmth or understanding? Stay and let your own unique rhythm remind the world you are far more than just another item to be ignored.",
